name: Ur'Ru'r
Lore: 'Fierce Tusken Raider. Ransacks homes and moisture farms on the borders of Mos Espa.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. While at Tusken Canyon, Jundland Wastes or same Tatooine site as UroRRuR''R''R, adds 2 to each of your battle destiny draws at Tatooine sites where you have a Tusken Raider.',
